-- Phoxta platform — 0030 seed the Travel business (multi-vertical booking)
-- Travel is a multi-vertical store: stays, experiences, cars, flights. Each listing
-- is a products row tagged by metadata.vertical (price_cents = rate, stock = units/
-- seats); every booking is a reservations row (migration 0028). Flights are modeled
-- as a fare = product (stock = seats) with a depart->return reservation
-- (units = passengers). Sets the buyer subdomain namespace (*.travel.phoxta.com)
-- and seeds a travel-demo tenant. Future travel buyers auto-seed this catalogue.
-- Idempotent on slug 'travel-demo'.

